description         Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::ReportPrereqs - Report on prerequisite versions during automated testing

long_description    This Dist::Zilla plugin adds a t/00-report-prereqs.t \
                    test file and an accompanying t/00-report-prereqs.dd \
                    data file. It reports the version of all modules listed \
                    in the distribution metadata prerequisites (including \
                    'recommends', 'suggests', etc.).

